## 五、常见命名错误与修正

### 5.1 错误示例 vs 正确示例

```dax
// ❌ 错误：使用特殊字符和空格
Table 1 = ...
Column 1 = ...
Sales Amount (USD) = ...

// ✅ 正确：使用下划线或驼峰命名
Table_1 = ...
Column_1 = ...
SalesAmount_USD = ...

// ❌ 错误：模糊的命名
Data = ...
Info = ...
Calc1 = ...

// ✅ 正确：描述性命名
Customer_Demographics = ...
Product_Information = ...
Revenue_Growth_Calculation = ...

// ❌ 错误：不一致的大小写
totalSales = ...
Total_Sales = ...
TOTAL_SALES = ...

// ✅ 正确：统一的大小写风格
total_sales = ...      // 全小写+下划线
TotalSales = ...       // 驼峰命名
TOTAL_SALES = ...      // 全大写（常量）
```

### 5.2 保留字冲突

```dax
// ❌ 错误：使用DAX保留字
Date = ...        // Date是DAX函数
Name = ...        // Name可能冲突
Value = ...       // Value是DAX函数

// ✅ 正确：添加前缀或使用不同名称
Dim_Date = ...
CustomerName = ...
SalesValue = ...
```

## 六、实际项目中的命名约定示例

### 6.1 电商数据分析项目

```dax
// ============ 表命名 ============
Dim_Date
Dim_Customer
Dim_Product
Dim_Store
Dim_Promotion
Fact_Sales
Fact_Inventory
Fact_WebLogs

// ============ 列命名 ============
// 主键
Dim_Customer[CustomerKey]
Dim_Product[ProductKey]
Fact_Sales[SalesKey]

// 业务键
Dim_Customer[CustomerID]
Dim_Product[ProductSKU]

// 属性
Dim_Customer[FirstName]
Dim_Customer[LastName]
Dim_Customer[Email]
Dim_Customer[SignupDate]

// 度量值
Sales[Total Revenue] = SUM(Fact_Sales[SalesAmount])
Sales[Total Quantity] = SUM(Fact_Sales[Quantity])
Sales[Average Price] = AVERAGE(Fact_Sales[UnitPrice])

// KPI度量值
KPIs[Revenue Growth YoY] = 
VAR CurrentRevenue = [Total Revenue]
VAR PreviousRevenue = CALCULATE([Total Revenue], SAMEPERIODLASTYEAR(Dim_Date[Date]))
RETURN
DIVIDE(CurrentRevenue - PreviousRevenue, PreviousRevenue)

KPIs[Customer Lifetime Value] = 
DIVIDE([Total Revenue], DISTINCTCOUNT(Fact_Sales[CustomerKey]))
```

